### <%= @class_header %> : show_shadow()
``` lua
local <%= @variable_text %>	-- example <%= @variable_text %>
<%= @variable_text %>:show_shadow( true )
```

If `true`, causes the <%= @class_name %> to draw a shadow on the <%= @link_tile %> underneath it.<br>
Otherwise it does _not_ draw a shadow underneath it.

#### Function Call
`<%= @variable_text %>:show_shadow( draw_shadow )`

#### Parameters
**`boolean`** `draw_shadow`<br>
	&emsp;_`true` if this <%= @class_name %> should have a shadow underneath it. Otherwise `false`._
